WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.790
Hey, good morning, family. How y'all been

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:06.710
doing? I'm going to go over a word

00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:10.030
that I gave 10 months ago.

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:13.070
It was on one of the big prophecy

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:14.829
channels, and they were talking about it,

00:00:14.829 --> 00:00:14.839
questioning

00:00:14.839 --> 00:00:17.150
whether

00:00:17.150 --> 00:00:17.160
it

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:19.310
was

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:22.429
really a real visit or a

00:00:22.439 --> 00:00:24.429
vision from the Lord.

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:27.269
Rightfully so, there's a lot of

00:00:27.279 --> 00:00:29.710
flaky stuff on YouTube, but I'm going

00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:33.389
to tell you this: it's genuine, it's real,

00:00:33.399 --> 00:00:35.950
and the Spirit of the Lord spoke to me

00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:38.630
just like He does many times.

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.950
I honestly

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:44.990
don't even watch

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.189
these channels that talk about

00:00:47.199 --> 00:00:49.549
this stuff because

00:00:49.559 --> 00:00:52.069
I'm very sensitive to the

00:00:52.079 --> 00:00:53.990
Spirit of God, and there are a lot of

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:56.709
false prophets out there. Whenever I

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:58.630
hear it, immediately I know if that is

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:02.229
not the Lord or if it

00:01:02.229 --> 00:01:02.239
is the Lord.

00:01:02.239 --> 00:01:04.189
If I get a mixed bag on that channel, I

00:01:04.199 --> 00:01:06.310
don't go back to it. I'm just

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:08.390
saying. People ask who it

00:01:08.390 --> 00:01:08.400
is, but

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:11.270
that's between you and God.

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:12.830
I'm not going to tell you who I believe

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:15.710
is a false prophet on YouTube;

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:17.070
that's just not

00:01:17.080 --> 00:01:20.270
what we're going to do. What I

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:24.350
want to tell you is

00:01:24.350 --> 00:01:24.360
that

00:01:24.360 --> 00:01:28.149
after taking time to

00:01:28.159 --> 00:01:29.910
pray over this—it's been about

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:31.550
11 months since I gave

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:33.270
this

00:01:33.270 --> 00:01:33.280
word—I

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:36.749
asked

00:01:36.759 --> 00:01:39.310
the Lord what He showed me

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:42.030
about the big asteroid. I

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:43.910
believe that Tom Horn gave that

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:45.510
word before he went home to be with the

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:48.910
Lord about Apophis, which I believe is Wormwood.

00:01:48.920 --> 00:01:50.670
It talks about it in the Book

00:01:50.680 --> 00:01:51.990
of Revelation, that there will be a

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.670
massive asteroid that hits the Earth. I

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:56.510
believe that what the Lord

00:01:56.520 --> 00:02:00.429
showed me was this massive asteroid that

00:02:00.439 --> 00:02:03.350
is scheduled to hit in

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:05.709
2029. It's supposed to hit the planet

00:02:05.719 --> 00:02:08.550
Earth and it's going to be

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:11.430
huge; supposedly,

00:02:14.120 --> 00:02:15.750
NASA has even talked about it

00:02:15.750 --> 00:02:15.760
being

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:19.990
ginormous. I

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.470
want to go

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:23.430
over again what the Lord

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:26.990
showed me. I was standing outside

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:28.869
praying,

00:02:28.869 --> 00:02:28.879
and

00:02:28.879 --> 00:02:31.509
I had

00:02:31.519 --> 00:02:34.509
an open-eyed vision. When this

00:02:34.519 --> 00:02:36.509
happened, it was

00:02:36.519 --> 00:02:41.190
so real that

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:46.910
I could actually hear it

00:02:46.920 --> 00:02:49.070
at the same time I

00:02:49.070 --> 00:02:49.080
was seeing

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:52.270
in the spirit this massive event.

00:02:54.519 --> 00:02:55.670
I was

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.910
standing by a carport and all of a

00:02:57.920 --> 00:03:02.869
sudden, this massive asteroid came. It was so

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:06.990
fast and so loud it deafened your

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.229
ears because the sonic boom was so

00:03:09.239 --> 00:03:12.430
powerful.

00:03:14.799 --> 00:03:19.509
It was the size

00:03:19.519 --> 00:03:23.670
of a major building, a

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:27.990
humongous rock. It came

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:30.509
out of the sky and shook

00:03:30.519 --> 00:03:33.149
everything, breaking the windows of all the

00:03:33.159 --> 00:03:35.470
houses.

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:38.470
It was moving so fast

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:39.910
you could barely see

00:03:39.910 --> 00:03:39.920
it—like

00:03:39.920 --> 00:03:42.910
a fireball with a humongous

00:03:42.920 --> 00:03:45.550
fire trail behind it.

00:03:47.959 --> 00:03:50.630
It was

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:53.030
shaking your whole entire being as it

00:03:53.030 --> 00:03:53.040
came

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:56.429
in from

00:03:56.439 --> 00:03:59.869
the West to

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:02.710
the East.

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:05.069
When

00:04:05.079 --> 00:04:07.630
it came

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:11.830
in, it crashed out by San Juan, Puerto

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:15.149
Rico. The

00:04:15.159 --> 00:04:18.509
United States government was trying to

00:04:18.519 --> 00:04:21.509
shoot this massive asteroid down, but because

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:24.430
it was moving so quickly, they could not hit

00:04:24.430 --> 00:04:24.440
it

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:26.310
with a rocket.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:28.990
They tried to

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:33.029
hit it with a massive green laser

00:04:33.039 --> 00:04:36.029
beam.

00:04:38.919 --> 00:04:40.790
In the spirit, I could see this beam

00:04:40.790 --> 00:04:40.800
come

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:43.790
out of the Alabama-New Orleans area.

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:46.110
I don't know if there's a massive

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:49.230
laser beam like that down by the

00:04:49.230 --> 00:04:49.240
Gulf

00:04:49.240 --> 00:04:52.830
area, but the beam shot across America.

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:56.629
Whenever

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:02.390
it

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:07.189
hit

00:05:08.919 --> 00:05:11.189
over

00:05:11.199 --> 00:05:15.510
the

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:20.469
Tennessee-Kentucky

00:05:20.479 --> 00:05:23.909
area, they hit it with

00:05:23.919 --> 00:05:26.790
that laser.

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:29.990
It cut it in half, but it didn't destroy

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:32.590
it;

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:35.110
it

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:37.950
split into three pieces.

00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:42.950
Those

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:45.870
pieces hit the Earth, and while I don't

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:48.590
remember where they all hit, the major

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:51.870
part of that rock hit by San Juan, Puerto

00:05:51.880 --> 00:05:54.309
Rico. The

00:05:54.319 --> 00:05:58.909
impact was so

00:05:58.919 --> 00:06:03.670
massive it sent a humongous tidal wave.

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:07.390
I

00:06:07.400 --> 00:06:09.150
tried

00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:11.110
to give an estimate

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:13.430
last time, saying it

00:06:13.440 --> 00:06:15.710
was several hundred feet high, but it

00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:15.720
was much

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:18.110
more than that.

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:32.870
It covered all the

00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:36.390
islands, including the Bahamas.

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:39.029
There was a massive tsunami wave that

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:41.270
came up out of the ocean at the speed

00:06:41.270 --> 00:06:41.280
of sound. It was

00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:43.790
so fast

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:51.909
that people did not have time

00:06:51.919 --> 00:06:55.309
to evacuate. I saw the

00:06:55.319 --> 00:06:58.749
water covering all the islands:

00:06:58.759 --> 00:07:02.510
St. Martin, St. Thomas, San

00:07:02.510 --> 00:07:02.520
Juan,

00:07:02.520 --> 00:07:08.350
Haiti,

00:07:08.350 --> 00:07:08.360
Cuba—all

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:11.029
were

00:07:11.039 --> 00:07:14.629
completely saturated

00:07:14.639 --> 00:07:17.589
and wiped out.

00:07:17.599 --> 00:07:19.270
If you weren't

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:22.430
high in the mountains,

00:07:22.430 --> 00:07:22.440
you

00:07:22.440 --> 00:07:24.390
were

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:27.029
destroyed. The

00:07:27.039 --> 00:07:30.070
wave came into

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:34.589
Florida, hitting Miami, Fort Lauderdale, and the

00:07:34.589 --> 00:07:34.599
whole Atlantic

00:07:34.599 --> 00:07:36.990
coast.

00:07:40.879 --> 00:07:44.869
This massive tsunami came

00:07:51.039 --> 00:07:54.710
miles inland,

00:08:01.110 --> 00:08:01.120
wiping

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:10.469
out major

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:13.350
hotels and houses on

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:15.309
the Atlantic

00:08:15.319 --> 00:08:18.309
seaboard.

00:08:18.319 --> 00:08:21.070
It went all the way up to Cape

00:08:21.070 --> 00:08:21.080
Hatteras

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:23.749
Island in North Carolina.

00:08:23.759 --> 00:08:26.070
Part of

00:08:26.080 --> 00:08:28.430
the tsunami went clear into Africa and

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:31.790
Europe, wiping out places in

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:34.070
England.

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.389
It was moving

00:08:44.389 --> 00:08:44.399
so

00:08:44.399 --> 00:08:46.870
quickly that people didn't have time to

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:50.630
evacuate and

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:52.310
were caught up in the water.

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:54.870
This was a

00:08:54.880 --> 00:08:58.590
very powerful experience.

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:08.269
I believe this is Wormwood;

00:09:08.279 --> 00:09:10.870
I really believe this is

00:09:10.880 --> 00:09:14.470
Apophis.

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:16.509
A lot of people say

00:09:16.519 --> 00:09:18.470
that it is

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:22.430
supposed to miss the Earth in 2029,

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:24.030
but

00:09:24.040 --> 00:09:26.790
I believe we're going to

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:30.190
have a direct impact soon.

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:32.790
Whether

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:34.310
the Rapture of the church has

00:09:34.310 --> 00:09:34.320
taken

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:37.190
place first or

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:39.190
this is part of it, I don't know.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:48.710
I'm not a Bible scholar; I

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:50.870
just pray and

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:53.190
the Lord shows me things to

00:09:53.200 --> 00:09:55.710
warn people that Jesus is coming.

00:09:58.399 --> 00:10:00.509
These are the

00:10:00.519 --> 00:10:02.910
signs of the times. We are in the

00:10:02.920 --> 00:10:05.550
last of the last days.

00:10:05.550 --> 00:10:05.560
We

00:10:05.560 --> 00:10:08.710
are

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:10.790
getting so close to the coming of

00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:13.150
the Lord Jesus Christ. This was an

00:10:13.150 --> 00:10:13.160
actual thing that

00:10:13.160 --> 00:10:15.430
the Lord showed me

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:32.350
in prayer.

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:53.829
If

00:10:53.839 --> 00:10:56.870
you hear the voice

00:10:56.880 --> 00:10:59.590
of the Lord telling you to move

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:02.269
out of a certain area, you need to listen

00:11:02.279 --> 00:11:05.389
to Him. We are going to experience things

00:11:05.399 --> 00:11:08.710
we've never thought we would see

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:11.230
in the coming days.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:15.829
I believe Jesus is coming sooner

00:11:15.839 --> 00:11:19.150
than many think, but nobody knows the

00:11:19.160 --> 00:11:20.790
day or the hour.

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:27.829
Have an expectation inside of

00:11:27.839 --> 00:11:29.750
you for His coming.

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:31.870
Be

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:34.310
excited

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.829
and

00:11:36.839 --> 00:11:40.550
have a sense of urgency,

00:11:40.560 --> 00:11:43.150
like Noah was

00:11:43.150 --> 00:11:43.160
when

00:11:43.160 --> 00:11:45.310
he was building the ark.

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:49.910
As in the days of Noah, so

00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:52.230
will it be when the Son of Man returns.

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:56.069
Only

00:11:56.079 --> 00:11:58.430
eight people entered the ark

00:11:58.430 --> 00:11:58.440
then;

00:12:00.829 --> 00:12:00.839
people

00:12:00.839 --> 00:12:04.310
were

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:06.790
not

00:12:06.800 --> 00:12:09.030
expecting the

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:11.150
flood.

00:12:14.519 --> 00:12:17.590
Today, people

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:20.590
are not expecting Jesus to come back.

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:23.189
Their hearts have become

00:12:23.199 --> 00:12:25.870
hardened

00:12:25.870 --> 00:12:25.880
and

00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:28.310
they

00:12:28.310 --> 00:12:28.320
seek

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:31.110
fleshly things. They

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:35.670
have an appearance of

00:12:35.680 --> 00:12:37.629
godliness but deny the power

00:12:37.639 --> 00:12:42.189
thereof. Many have itching ears.

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:47.030
Even in the body of Christ,

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:48.389
the church hasn't preached the truth

00:12:48.389 --> 00:12:48.399
of

00:12:48.399 --> 00:12:49.470
holiness

00:12:49.480 --> 00:12:52.389
and repentance. They've

00:12:52.399 --> 00:12:54.310
fallen away into a

00:12:54.310 --> 00:12:54.320
seeker-friendly gospel—milky words

00:12:54.320 --> 00:12:56.509
with a little

00:12:56.519 --> 00:12:58.310
porridge.

00:12:58.320 --> 00:12:59.990
The body of Christ in

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:01.870
those churches is anemic

00:13:01.870 --> 00:13:01.880
and

00:13:01.880 --> 00:13:04.310
starving spiritually.

00:13:15.839 --> 00:13:18.430
I'm telling you, Jesus is coming

00:13:18.440 --> 00:13:20.629
soon. I hope you're watching

00:13:20.639 --> 00:13:22.829
for Him and your heart is ready.

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:25.790
We're going to

00:13:25.800 --> 00:13:28.870
see signs in the heavens,

00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:30.710
and this is a

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:32.590
major sign prophesied

00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:35.870
in the Bible.

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:45.870
Father, I thank You for every

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:48.069
person

00:13:48.079 --> 00:13:50.710
watching,

00:13:50.720 --> 00:13:52.790
excited about the coming of

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:55.509
Your Son. Thank You, Lord,

00:13:55.509 --> 00:13:55.519
that

00:13:55.519 --> 00:13:59.269
Jesus

00:13:59.279 --> 00:14:01.590
died for us and

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:04.150
rose again

00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:07.269
so

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:08.870
that we don't have to

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:11.590
go to a devil's hell.

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:45.710
We have an expectation of

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:48.829
Your Son's soon return.

00:14:54.040 --> 00:14:56.430
We are looking for You daily, keeping

00:14:56.440 --> 00:14:59.990
our lamps full of oil.

00:15:09.279 --> 00:15:11.150
I know there will be a lot of lives

00:15:11.160 --> 00:15:13.030
lost as the Book of Revelation

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:15.829
tells us, but I

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:17.509
thank You that You said You didn't

00:15:17.519 --> 00:15:19.670
want any to perish.

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:22.350
I thank

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:25.670
You that people are repenting

00:15:25.680 --> 00:15:27.870
and coming

00:15:27.880 --> 00:15:30.949
closer to You today.

00:15:38.720 --> 00:15:40.629
If

00:15:40.639 --> 00:15:43.389
we're here when Apophis hits, I thank

00:15:43.399 --> 00:15:47.550
You, Lord, that believers will hear

00:15:47.550 --> 00:15:47.560
Your voice

00:15:47.560 --> 00:15:49.870
and You

00:15:49.870 --> 00:15:49.880
will

00:15:49.880 --> 00:15:51.749
quicken

00:15:51.759 --> 00:15:53.150
their spirits to get out

00:15:57.230 --> 00:15:57.240
quickly.

00:16:01.639 --> 00:16:03.949
We give

00:16:03.959 --> 00:16:06.590
You all the glory, honor, and praise.

00:16:06.600 --> 00:16:08.949
In the

00:16:08.959 --> 00:16:11.230
mighty name of Jesus,

00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:14.550
amen.

